'''Imbata''' ni [[igikoko]] gifise amababa nk'inyoni, kikagira umunwa ufyase kandi muremure.

Imbata zikunda ahantu kenshi hari amazi, zimwe mbere usanga zibera mumazi, mugihe izindi ziba kw'isi zorowe cane cane n'abantu mumihana.

Mubijanye no kurondoka, imbata zirata amagi kurya kw'inkoko, zikabundikira hama inyuma y'ikiringo zikaberura ya magi akavamwo imiswi y'imbata.

